Dear voters

Notary nodes Season 3 has just started, and I'm already preparing the 10% distribution of my KMD mining gains, as promised, which will be sent on august 15th or 16th (10 more percent will go to @mrlynch).

In the beginning of june, Agama has been hacked (see https://support.komodoplatform.com/support/solutions/articles/29000029932-agama-security-announcement), and therefore, some of your addresses has been compromised.

As I don't want to make the hacker richer than (s)he is, I checked explorer to find new addresses to send the rewards to.
Those addresses are the ones you told the Komomodo team to refund to.
(see https://support.komodoplatform.com/support/solutions/articles/29000029973-steps-to-reclaim-funds-after-the-agama-incident)

In the following message, you'll see in the first column the address you sent your VOTE2019 tokens from, and in the second one, the address I'll send the rewards to.
Feel free to DM before august 15th in case there's a problem with new addresses.

Thanks for your support!
